\q1  
\v 3 Xulunyumi baa to Isirayila …≤ama to, 
\q1 a naxa rabi mafuren. 
\q1 Yurud…õn xure to e to fa ra, a man naxa kira fi e ma. 
\q1  
\v 4 Isirayila geyae to e to, e naxa tugan tugan …≤…õl…õxinyi ra, 
